Name: Chezzle
About the game: Chezzle is an endless Chess puzzler with a twist. By becoming the piece that you capture, you'll need to plan ahead and try chain together moves to clear the board. The game has been carefully crafted with healing and meditation in mind. Chezzle features over 18 relaxing soundtracks, as well as rain effects to boot. Get lost in the world of Chezzle, a thought provoking experience.
